What you need to know:  Achieng' got the prestigious monthly award after retaining her title in Nairobi by beating Zimbabwean Chiedza "Queen Tiger" Homakoma in the eighth of the scheduled 10 rounds in December last yearThe hard-hitting boxer beat top nominees among them Chess National champion Mehul Gohil, tennis Roselida Asumwa, who reached Rwanda Open singles final and won Rwanda Open doubles title partnering with her twin sister Angella Okutoyi, and Collins Ndunda who won three medals at the Mombasa international Tong-IL-Moo-Do Championship